  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is evaluate the efficacy, safety, and pharmacokinetics of weekly
      intravenous infusions of 1 mg/kg recombinant human N-acetylgalactosamine 4-sulfatase (rhASB)
      in patients diagnosed with Mucopolysaccharidosis VI (MPS VI)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
